metadata.name: Paternidad
metadata.description:
"Paternidad" means fatherhood in Spanish. Two clouds travel together in an inexistent place where our memories and dreams can be laid down.  Through this desolated landscape, we find comfort in each other's company. Thank you for your very existence .-

Photomontage produced in  December 2021. Captures made in February 2021.

The first collector is offered a certified limited edition archival print.

4000x4000
